title: Bobby On Masks Not Being Required + Keith Urban Plays The Hits In Studio! + Raymundo vs 'The Queen of Facts’
itunes:title: Bobby On Masks Not Being Required + Keith Urban Plays The Hits In Studio! + Raymundo vs 'The Queen of Facts’
description:
Bobby on how he feels about the mask mandate being lifted for people who are fully vaccinated. Keith Urban stops by to play a few of his hits for us! He also talks about getting a new tattoo, Taylor Swift texting him to be a part of her album and performs something special as a surprise to Bobby. Raymundo tries to take down Amy who is known as the “Queen of Facts” in a Fun Fact Friday Off!
